    "3 | MODIFY designs high-quality combinatorial starting libraries for GB1.",
    "a The 3D structure (PDB: 1PGA) of GB1.",
    "The four residues mutated to create combinatorial libraries are colored in blue.",
    "b The Pareto frontier of MODIFY library designs on GB1, with each point representing a library corresponding to a diversity strength λ.",
